---
/**
 * WhatHappensNext — 3-step follow-up process. Reusable standalone component.
 * Horizontal on desktop (3 col grid), vertical on mobile.
 */
---
<section class="space-y-8 md:grid md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-8 md:space-y-0" aria-label="What happens next">
  <div>
    <span class="font-data mb-1 block text-sm font-bold text-gold">01</span>
    <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-dark mb-1">Get Your Quote</h3>
    <p class="font-body text-sm text-dark/60">
      Fill out the quick form or give us a call. We can usually quote right over the phone — no site visit required in most cases.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <span class="font-data mb-1 block text-sm font-bold text-gold">02</span>
    <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-dark mb-1">Design Together on Install Day</h3>
    <p class="font-body text-sm text-dark/60">
      When we arrive, we walk the yard with you to finalize the layout, colors, and patterns before any work begins.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <span class="font-data mb-1 block text-sm font-bold text-gold">03</span>
    <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-dark mb-1">Professional Installation</h3>
    <p class="font-body text-sm text-dark/60">
      Our crew handles everything — prep, install, cleanup. Most projects are completed the very same day.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
